sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Thread A
    participant M1 as alice (ID 3)
    participant M2 as bob (ID 7)
    participant B as Thread B

    Note over A,B: Both threads want alice and bob
    A->>M1: lock alice first
    B->>M1: try alice — blocks
    M1-->>A: acquired
    A->>M2: lock bob
    M2-->>A: acquired
    Note over A: work done, release both
    M1-->>B: acquired (unblocked)
    B->>M2: lock bob
    M2-->>B: acquired
